    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 12'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='800' maxwidth='1500' minheight='800' minwidth='1500' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98000' id='3' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
            <zone fixed-size='744' forceUpdate='true' h='94000' id='5' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='18'>Financial Analytics: The Cost of Capacity Constraints</run>
                <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='14'>Core Insights &amp; Data Trends:</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='15'>•</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Stagnant Revenue Trend:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> The top line chart shows that combined monthly revenue has flattened, fluctuating strictly between $41M and $43M over the entire period with no meaningful upward trajectory.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Disproportionate Resource Return:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> The bottom right chart shows that revenue fails to reflect operational burden. Psychiatry generates the lowest revenue return in the hospital despite consuming massive bed days.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>The Margin Erosion:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> While Pulmonology shows strong topline revenue, the high readmission risk and long stays discovered earlier act as a major financial drain, eroding actual profit margins.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='14'>Impact on Hospital Operations:&#10;</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Capacity-Driven Stagnation:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> Because beds are locked up by long-staying Psychiatry patients and repeating Pulmonology readmissions, the hospital cannot turn over beds to admit new cases, causing the revenue stagnation.
</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Financial Impact:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> The operational bottlenecks in these two specific subspecialties are directly capping the hospital&apos;s earning potential, proving that bed shortages are fundamentally driving the financial crisis.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                <format attr='background-color' value='#f3f4f6' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
