    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 15'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='800' maxwidth='1500' minheight='800' minwidth='1500' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98000' id='3' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
            <zone fixed-size='712' forceUpdate='true' h='90000' id='5' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='18'>Recommendations: Financial Leadership</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='14'>
Strategic Actions &amp; Investments:
</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Prioritize Investment in High-Burden Service Lines:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> Allocate resources toward specialties generating the greatest operational pressure to support staffing, patient management, and discharge planning initiatives aimed at reducing avoidable costs.
</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Align Financial Planning with Operational Demand:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> Ensure future budgeting and resource allocation decisions reflect actual patient demand patterns, particularly within specialties contributing most significantly to bed occupancy and patient flow pressures.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='14'>Immediate Quantifications for the Finance Team:
</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Quantify the Cost of Extended Stays:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> Determine the daily financial impact of occupied inpatient beds within high-burden specialties such as Pulmonology and Psychiatry. This will help leadership understand how prolonged stays affect hospital capacity and revenue performance.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Quantify the Cost of Readmissions:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> Calculate the financial burden associated with repeat admissions, including additional treatment costs, bed utilization, and resource consumption. This will help establish the true financial impact of high-readmission diagnoses.</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#f3f4f6' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
