    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 8'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='800' maxwidth='1500' minheight='800' minwidth='1500' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98000' id='3' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
            <zone fixed-size='517' forceUpdate='true' h='65625' id='5' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='18'>Operational Diagnostics: Volume vs. Capacity Pressures</run>
                <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='14'>Core Insights &amp; Data Trends:</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• </run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Seasonal Inpatient Volume: The top trend line tracks total encounter volume over time, representing the distinct number of individual inpatient admissions and clinical care processes managed by the hospital over the past 24 months.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>The data shows predictable seasonal surges, peaking at 94 encounters in January and 96 encounters in December, which aligns with standard end of year and winter illness trends.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Outside of these expected seasonal influxes, baseline volume remains relatively consistent throughout the mid year months.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>This proves that systemic operational pressure is not driven by an influx of new patient numbers.</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#f3f4f6' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
