    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Operational dashboard story'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='800' maxwidth='1500' minheight='800' minwidth='1500' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98000' id='3' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
            <zone h='77375' id='5' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='77375' id='6' type-v2='text' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='18'>Business Context</run>
                  <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Over the past </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>24 months</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>, leadership at </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Zion Tech Hub Facility</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> has become increasingly concerned about the hospital&apos;s ability to efficiently manage patient </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>flow across the inpatient system.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Despite continued patient activity, several departments have reported challenges in moving patients through the inpatient system. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>This has raised significant concerns regarding:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>The </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>operational performance</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> of the inpatient system.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Its impact on </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>patient outcomes</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Its impact on </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>financial sustainability</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>As these concerns continued to emerge across the organization, leadership commissioned a </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>review of inpatient activity</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> to better understand the factors affecting patient flow and overall hospital operations.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#f3f4f6' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
        <devicelayout auto-generated='true' name='Phone'>
          <size maxheight='700' minheight='700' sizing-mode='vscroll' />
          <zones>
            <zone h='100000' id='22' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
              <zone h='84000' id='21' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='84000' x='8000' y='8000'>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='77375' id='6' type-v2='text' w='98934' x='533' y='1000'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='18'>Business Context</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Over the past </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>24 months</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>, leadership at </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Zion Tech Hub Facility</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> has become increasingly concerned about the hospital&apos;s ability to efficiently manage patient </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>flow across the inpatient system.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Despite continued patient activity, several departments have reported challenges in moving patients through the inpatient system. </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>This has raised significant concerns regarding:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>The </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>operational performance</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> of the inpatient system.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Its impact on </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>patient outcomes</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>Its impact on </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>financial sustainability</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>As these concerns continued to emerge across the organization, leadership commissioned a </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>review of inpatient activity</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'> to better understand the factors affecting patient flow and overall hospital operations.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
